Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去便利店一趟 你要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脆脆君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是指晚饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我做饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说得这么恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也有在练习做饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这话等你练好了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就随便买点？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是就在这里吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消除完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无色之色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其纯粹而冰凉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ef - a tale of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有 不想忘却的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.54,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.75,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:29.13,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:35.97,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:42.23,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:48.69,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:55.15,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:01:00.95,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:07.88,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.92,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:17.13,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:23.56,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:26.73,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:30.27,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:36.70,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:01:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 我坚信
